        "text": "This has occurred in our teams too. Spontaneously across all users and sites consistent with the recent Chrome update. We have many coders using a mixture of WebStorm 9, 10, and EAP and cannot hit breakpoints set in original sources.\n\nOur build is [http://angularity.github.com Angularity] (browserify with babeljs). Generated source maps are impeccable. For example, see the 'todo' example project in the 'getting started' section.\n\nWebStorm breakpoints work in compiled files. Chrome breakpoints work in original sources. Neither are satisfactory. Tried [https://www.jetbrains.com/webstorm/help/debugging-javascript.html#d241502e355 firefox debug] but could not make it work.\n\nThis will become a major fail for Webstorm if not quickly addressed.",
