        "text": "@develar The example project used if very small and not representative of an average project. As Sergey mentioned his tests had a delay of two seconds, mine had a delay of twenty seconds, using node-inspector I had very quick startups too. This is almost a deal breaker for me so I can't understand why nobody is going to look at this, it would also be good to understand why it is not a 'Webstorm issue', I have added and removed many npm packages and still have the same results. ",
