        "parentId": null,
        "deleted": false,
        "jiraId": null,
        "text": "From the dump it looks like the toolwindow showing the current file structure is open and its loading takes a lot of time (likely due to a bug). If you close this view (it's usually on the bottom left) quickly after startup, the performance might improve.",
        "shownForIssueAuthor": false,
